### DEMO SEQUENCE (For Presentation)
### ======================================

### DEMO 1: Success Case (Establish Baseline)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Demo",
  "email": "alice.demo@example.com",
  "userType": 0
}

### DEMO 2: Validation Errors (Multiple Fields)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "A",
  "lastName": "",
  "email": "bad-email",
  "userType": 0
}

### DEMO 3: Duplicate Email (Conflict)
# Run this twice to show conflict handling
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Charlie",
  "lastName": "Conflict",
  "email": "charlie.conflict@example.com",
  "userType": 0
}

### DEMO 4: JSON Parse Error (Missing Comma)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "David"
  "lastName": "ParseError",
  "email": "david@example.com",
  "userType": 0
}
